Title: Usually new model releases fill me with a sense of dread. Of the time until the singularity burning ...
Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: Usually new model releases fill me with a sense of dread. Of the time until the singularity burning away. Of having one more task to do (try it out in a variety of pipelines and personally). But for some reason new Sonnet has given me a lot of energy. Everything feels possible
